        },
        "rich_text_9LDfB8": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Why Many Buyers Are Rediscovering Vintage Details",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>Why Many Buyers Are Rediscovering Vintage Details</h2><p>In recent years, many jewellery buyers have moved away from overly simple designs. Instead, they are looking for rings with character.</p><p>Vintage techniques like milgrain, filigree, and engraving add exactly that.</p><p>These details create a sense of artistry that you don’t often see in modern minimalist rings. They also help a ring stand out without needing a large diamond or heavy design.</p><p>For people who appreciate craftsmanship and subtle elegance, vintage-style rings offer something truly special.</p>",
            "custom_id": "why-many",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        }
